</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="banner">
            <div class="banner-text">
              <p>CodeNames     ◐     CodeNames     ◓     CodeNames     ◑     CodeNames     ◒     CodeNames     ◐     CodeNames     ◓     CodeNames     ◑     CodeNames     ◒     CodeNames     ◐     CodeNames     ◓     CodeNames      ◑     CodeNames     ◒     CodeNames</p>
